japan 's 1986/87 sugar cane output seen fall an agricultur ministri survey ha estim the nation 's 1986/87 crop sugar cane output at 2.14 mln tonn , down from 2.62 mln a year earlier . ministri offici said the declin wa due to bad weather and a reduct in the land under sugar cane thi season , which total 34,800 hectar , down from 35,700 in 1985/86 , they said . harvest stretch from decemb 1986 to april 1987 japan 's final output will be announc at the begin of june , they said .